68d32abc88ea7e5aadf627fe0239cc41","tid":50143,"uid":20286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用左就3年都無病無痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你認為洗唔洗買Apple care?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就過一年嗰陣買<br />\nMacbook壞一壞就好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cc66c9565c8072dff1f1c8dfcf3a49701c7c34","tid":50143,"uid":30857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"一般啦 部air用左2年半壞底版 仲諗住用到3-4年"},{"pid":"b4338bc4102d239d37363868267dd8fdb5d6d72b","tid":50143,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用左就3年都無病無痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你認為洗唔洗買Apple care?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買好啲<br />\n我部12年mbp用咗年幾就壞底板<br />\n返apple換，正價要四千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩買咗apple care<br />\n<br />\n不過換完底板之後就用到而家都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33dfda79fe761aea90014567cf05c63b6bb18cd5","tid":50143,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"win機都有ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前hardware最易死係os drive,用左ssd後好難壞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb417f9f9824ff60b9db3b5a06fc9216e2f42a49","tid":50143,"uid":55922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:47:41.000Z","msg":"仲用緊 2010 Mid MacBook Pro <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca2a479101062bc7162d2e0128a548a7050f303","tid":50143,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T21:10:20.000Z","msg":"14 mid 13&quot; mbpr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企插晒moon keyboard 當desktop 用<br />\n做嘢返學都用"},{"pid":"a15e967bcffae76a8d35012aab4441125e36addb","tid":50143,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T21:12:53.000Z","msg":"2012 MBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0291b4e8e93e820f4bafbe719f0e24e0991d00c1","tid":50143,"uid":50634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T21:34:14.000Z","msg":"13 MBP  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fd3d51e313d75ae60f829d15ea2e598ff11d2f","tid":50143,"uid":28061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T21:42:13.000Z","msg":"Mid 2014 mbpr <br />\n藍牙神神地，成日斷聲<br />\n冇買Apple care<br />\n唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84b00257e299376fe8b03c29901cc88656990f6","tid":50143,"uid":31166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T21:45:17.000Z","msg":"無買Apple Care真係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMACBOOK 都咁貴 仲要慳果小小<br />\n壞撚左仲貴"},{"pid":"67c5f3c52b4391ac03028dd4fdbc258b2015c971","tid":50143,"uid":17492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"用左4年幾 mbpr <br />\n未有換機意慾 係打唔倒機"},{"pid":"6e4098bb75be4cbe0ab633acf08e7ac059c8e900","tid":50143,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>win機都有ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前hardware最易死係os drive,用左ssd後好難壞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將屋企部兩年前買既win機換ssd，成部好似新買咁"},{"pid":"fd626ca4d1814b75fc7f6ed7ca8bb9d0f713904c","tid":50143,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"好多人都話mac唔會壞添<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過apple班市場部員工係有一手.所以先叫入教<br />\n<br />\n人地PC 世界興左好耐既野,都可以俾佢地作個名就講到係新野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然有D野係APPLE行先.不過PC果邊好少會係咁吹奏(依個可能同PC世界根本就係雜牌軍有關)"},{"pid":"232bee0c73dd6f9d1b68d0dc3aa2eb5eeb7cfbd0","tid":50143,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>win機都有ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前hardware最易死係os drive,用左ssd後好難壞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得信APPLE真係唔會壞既人根本就同話用AMD U既PC係好易死既人同一班人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最幾年NVIDIA粒GPU高溫,用到咁上下一定甩錫,搞到收皮(情況似XB360既三紅)<br />\n<br />\nAPPLE果邊都避唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你用同等價位買部WIN NB根本就差唔多玩法<br />\n<br />\n頂多係個OS比較好用.<br />\n<br />\n穩定性計,依加既WIN根本就差極有限"},{"pid":"19406d67a31df4fe62b6ba88ad61a00ef3b6be5a","tid":50143,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"三年冇事，除咗去旅行果幾日唔用，冇熄過機"},{"pid":"56dcc209a03df68c33ae0dcde24e50754caf5763","tid":50143,"uid":59136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>win機都有ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前hardware最易死係os drive,用左ssd後好難壞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得信APPLE真係唔會壞既人根本就同話用AMD U既PC係好易死既人同一班人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最幾年NVIDIA粒GPU高溫,用到咁上下一定甩錫,搞到收皮(情況似XB360既三紅)<br />\n<br />\nAPPLE果邊都避唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你用同等價位買部WIN NB根本就差唔多玩法<br />\n<br />\n頂多係個OS比較好用.<br />\n<br />\n穩定性計,依加既WIN根本就差極有限</blockquote><br />\nOS比較好用已經贏好多啦<br />\n（所以最抵玩係non-mac裝linux）<br />\n（利申macbook pro用家 不過會dual boot玩linux）"},{"pid":"46c79d6dbe4e1b2cc91812e